post.description:
Create prints containing parts and/or SKUs

This endpoint allows you to issue prints by specifying individual parts and/or complete SKUs (products).
Each part or SKU can be customized with specific quantities, parameters, materials, and other configuration options.

requestBody.description: - Build configuration specifying parts and SKUs to include

201.description: Result containing created part builds and SKU builds with their assigned IDs

200.description: Contains data, metadata, and query information

requestBody.description: Complex search query with filter conditions and settings

201.description: Response containing filtered parts data and metadata
